          "settings": {
            "heading": "Technical specifications",
            "text": "<p><strong>TREATMENT TIME: </strong>3 minutes<br/><strong>WAVELENGTH: </strong>633nm (Red), 830nm (Near-Infrared)<br/><strong>TREATMENT TIME: </strong>10 minutes<br/><strong>CHARGING TIME: </strong>4 hours<br/><strong>LEDs: </strong>55 dual core</p>"
